Cerro Amboró- - During this trip I climbed up the Río Isama to the summit of Cerro Amboró in Parque Nacional de Amboró. As the trail is not established and winds over ridges and dense forest I have little idea of the exact locality. Nevertheless today I collected between 1170 m and the summit at 1510 m. 60 km W. of Santa Cruz. A number of habitats collected: Tangled Clusia woodlands 1050-1200 m, Ericaceous-Clusia scrub 1170-1510 m, upper riverine woodlands 1250 m, grasslands cliffs 1300-1510 m. First botanical expedition to the actual summit.
